headline: Mondelez: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: CHICAGO (AP) — Mondelez International Inc. MDLZ) on Tuesday reported fourth-quarter net income of $665 million. On a per-share basis, the Chicago-based company said it had net income of 51 cents.

headline: Mondelez (NASDAQ:MDLZ) Exceeds Q4 CY2025 Expectations
summary: Packaged snacks company Mondelez (NASDAQ:MDLZ) reported Q4 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 9.3% year on year to $10.5 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.68 per share was 2.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
